commit.message:
Updates the DBus activation environment

We use dbus-update-activation-environment to update the list of
environment variables used by dbus-daemon --session.
Some applications might not work properly if the DBus variables are not set.

Assuming that the executable name is always `dbus-update-activation-environment`.

Closes https://github.com/lxqt/lxqt-runner/issues/265.
